《'''Pizza'''》是荷兰[[唱片骑师|DJ]]兼[[音乐制作人|音乐制作人]][[马丁·盖瑞斯|马丁·盖瑞斯]]创作的歌曲。歌曲于2017年8月25日通过[[戳印唱片|戳印唱片]]发行，并于同日在盖瑞斯出席的2017年[[明日世界电子音乐节|明日世界电子音乐节]]上进行首秀。

==背景==
盖瑞斯在2017年明日世界电子音乐节的闭幕曲中首次展示了《Pizza》。2017年7月30日，一名歌迷在[[推特|推特]]上向盖瑞斯询问歌曲名，盖瑞斯回答说：“歌名其实叫《披萨》。”（It's actually called Pizza.）<ref>{{cite news|last=Karlie|first=Powell|title=Watch Martin Garrix Close Out Tomorrowland 2017's Main Stage|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/07/31/watch-martin-garrix-close-tomorrowland-2017s-main-stage/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=Your EDM|date=2017-07-31|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408184106/https://www.youredm.com/2017/07/31/watch-martin-garrix-close-tomorrowland-2017s-main-stage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年8月10日，他在[[伊维萨岛|伊维萨岛]]表演的回顾视频中，使用了《Pizza》作为背景音乐<ref name="EDM Sauce 2">{{cite news|last=Erik|title=Martin Garrix Teases New Unreleased Track And It Sounds Incredible: Listen|url=https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/08/13/martin-garrix-teases-new-unreleased-track-sounds-incredible-listen/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=EDM Sauce|date=2017-08-13|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822182741/https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/08/13/martin-garrix-teases-new-unreleased-track-sounds-incredible-listen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年8月14日，在回复一位要求新音乐的歌迷时，他在推特上宣布将在未来两周内发布这首歌<ref>{{cite news|last=Anna|first=Hulton|title=Martin Garrix confirms he will be releasing new music very soon|url=https://planetradio.co.uk/hits/entertainment/music/martin-garrix-confirms-will-releasing-new-music-soon/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work={{tsl|en|Key 103||Key 103}}|date=2017-08-15|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822182605/https://planetradio.co.uk/hits/entertainment/music/martin-garrix-confirms-will-releasing-new-music-soon/}}</ref><ref name="Bagin Beats">{{cite news|last=Rajrishi|first=Murthi|title=Martin Garrix Announces His Stunning Tomorrowland Closing Track As His Next Release!|url=http://thebanginbeats.com/2017/08/martin-garrix-tomorrowland-closing-track-pizza-release/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=Bagin Beats|date=2017-08-16|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822175056/http://thebanginbeats.com/2017/08/martin-garrix-tomorrowland-closing-track-pizza-release/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他称这首歌是专门为明日世界电子音乐节而创作的<ref>{{cite news|last=Derek|first=Staples|title=Martin Garrix confirms release of Tomorrowland closing track|url=https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-confirms-release-tomorrowland-closing-track|accessdate=2017-08-23|work=DJ Mag|date=2017-08-15|archive-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823115710/https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-confirms-release-tomorrowland-closing-track|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Your EDM">{{cite news|last=Matthew|first=Meadow|title=Martin Garrix To Release His Tomorrowland Closing Song in The Next 2 Weeks|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/08/14/martin-garrix-release-tomorrowland-closing-song-next-2-weeks/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=Your EDM|date=2017-08-14|archive-date=2022-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220101135732/https://www.youredm.com/2017/08/14/martin-garrix-release-tomorrowland-closing-song-next-2-weeks/}}</ref><ref name="EDM Sauce">{{cite news|last=Grace|first=Wade|title=We Finally Have More Details on Martin Garrix's Upcoming Releases|url=https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/08/14/details-martin-garrixs-upcoming-releases/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=EDM Sauce|date=2017-08-14|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822182640/https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/08/14/details-martin-garrixs-upcoming-releases/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Angel|first=Park|title=Martin Garrix will officially drop his Tomorrowland closing track in 2 weeks!|url=http://www.ravejungle.com/2017/08/15/martin-garrix-tomorrowland-closing-track/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=Rave Jungle|date=2017-08-15|archive-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822181659/http://www.ravejungle.com/2017/08/15/martin-garrix-tomorrowland-closing-track/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年8月16日，盖瑞斯分享了这首歌的录音室版本，这是他在[[荷兰|荷兰]][[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]的工作室录制，他将标题取为“今天完成这首歌（我希望）”（"Finishing this song today (I hope),"）<ref name="Your EDM 2">{{cite news|last=Karlie|first=Powell|title=Martin Garrix Shares Official Teaser of Tomorrowland "Pizza" ID Coming Soon|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/08/17/martin-garrix-shares-official-teaser-tomorrowland-pizza-id-coming-soon/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=Your EDM|date=2017-08-17|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513122651/https://www.youredm.com/2017/08/17/martin-garrix-shares-official-teaser-tomorrowland-pizza-id-coming-soon/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Julian|title=Martin Garrix previews upcoming release 'Pizza'|url=http://www.edmtunes.com/2017/08/martin-garrix-upcoming-release-pizza/|accessdate=2017-08-23|work=EDMTunes|date=2017-08-16|archive-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823115008/http://www.edmtunes.com/2017/08/martin-garrix-upcoming-release-pizza/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在2017年8月20日回复一位粉丝时透露了这首歌的发行日期，当时粉丝问他是否完成制作<ref name="Your EDM 3">{{cite news|last=Matthew|first=Meadow|title=Martin Garrix "Pizza" Will Drop This Friday|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/08/21/martin-garrix-pizza-will-drop-friday/|accessdate=2017-08-22|work=Your EDM|date=2017-08-21|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507103537/https://www.youredm.com/2017/08/21/martin-garrix-pizza-will-drop-friday/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=David|first=Rishty|title=Martin Garrix Dropping New Song 'Pizza' on Friday, Returns With New Season of 'The Martin Garrix Show'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/7940878/martin-garrix-pizza-martin-garrix-show-season-2-video|accessdate=2017-08-23|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2017-08-22|archive-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825082623/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/7940878/martin-garrix-pizza-martin-garrix-show-season-2-video|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Derek|first=Staples|title=The Martin Garrix Show season two launches with new format: